<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1914-02-20T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1914-02-20T00:00:00-05:00" n="1479" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d1479">
                            <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 312.41/96.</note>
                            <head>
                                <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss>
                                    to Special Agent <persName type="to">Carothers</persName>.</hi>
                            </head>
                            <opener>
                                <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                            </opener>
                            <opener>
                                <dateline rendition="#right">
                                    <placeName>
                                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State</hi>, <lb/>
                                        <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1914-02-20">
                                        <hi rend="italic">February 20, 1914</hi></date>.</dateline>
                            </opener>
                            <p>Your February 20. Obtain without fail and forward to the Department
                                at your earliest convenience copy of sentence under which Benton is
                                said to have been executed. If not a violation of confidence you may
                                give to the press copy of court proceedings. Collaborate with
                                American Consul and telegraph after mass meeting statement embracing
                                all reliable information obtainable.</p>
                            <closer>
                                <signed>
                                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Bryan</hi></signed>.</closer>
                        </div>
                        </body></text></TEI>